Requirements:
1. Users and Access: The system should support two roles:<Implement authentication>
    ● Admin (Coordinator){View all fields, Monitor updates across agents}
    ● Field Agent{Update the stage of a field, Add notes or observations}

2. Field Management: The system should allow:
    ● Creating and managing fields
    ● Assigning fields to field agents
- field should have, at minimum:
● Name ● Crop type ● Planting date ● Current stage{Planted/Growing/Ready/Harvested}

3. Field Status Logic
Each field should have a computed status based on its data.
At minimum, handle:
● Active(if planted or growing or ready)
● At Risk(if planted over many days ago and no updated with like notes)
● Completed(if harvested)
Define and implement reasonable logic for how status is determined

